title: Facebook is pouring money into 2020 campaigns as antitrust investigations heat up
text:
An analysis by nonprofit MapLight finds that members of the House Judiciary Committee are receiving $1 out of every $12 donated by Facebook and its employees during the 2020 election cycle. 
 This story was produced by MapLight, a nonprofit organization that reveals the influence of money in politics, and published in partnership with Fast Company.
